Paper: hep-th/0106107

Date: 2001-06-13

Title: Proposal for Background Independent Berkovits' Superstring Field Theory

Authors: J. Kluson

Comments: 15 pages

Journal-ref: JHEP 0107 (2001) 039

In this paper we would like to propose the background independent formulationof Berkovits' superstring field theory. Then we will show that the solution ofequation of motion of this theory leads to the Berkovits' superstring fieldtheory formulated around particular CFT background.